POLAND: NBP OFFERS TO DRAIN PLN 300 MLN FOR 14 DAYS.NBP OFFERS TO DRAIN PLN 300 MLN FOR 14 DAYS.The National Bank of Polandoffered to drain 300 million zlotys, in nominal terms, off themarket for 14 days through a reverse NBP-bill repurchaseauction, the bank said.    Deadline hour		 - 12:00    Date of settlement	  - AUG 21, 1996    Repurchase		    - SEP 4, 1996    Discount rate (pct)	 - 20.00Maturity of bills offered - SEP 18, 1996-- Warsaw Newsroom +48 22 653 9700